description: Located in one of the most coveted sections of South Boston, this top floor home is on a quiet tree-lined street, just a five-minute walk to the beach, restaurants and shops. Pristine 2 bedroom, 2.5 bathroom upper duplex comprised of over 1,200 square feet of living space on two levels, plus private roof deck with oceans views across to the JFK Library. Kitchen, dining area, living room, half bath and laundry on main level. Upstairs, find two spacious bedrooms, each with ensuite full baths and a large walk-in closet in the master. In unit laundry, central AC, gas heat furnaced, hardwood flooring, granite counters, excellent ceiling height and generous closets make this a great place to call home. Small two unit condo association with one of the lowest condo fees you will see. Pristine condition just move right in.
